- GloFAS v4.0 reanalysis via EWDS (`cems-glofas-historical`), acquired $build_date.
- Copernicus DEM 30 m via AWS Open Data — $dem_tile_count tiles.
- ESA WorldCover 10 m — $worldcover_tile_count tile(s), $worldcover_vrt_note.
- Copernicus EMS rapid mapping — $ems_provenance.

